"<ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/docs/doc-primer/index.html\"> "
"dokumentacijo KDE</ulink> za namige o formatu DocBook."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Meanwhile, you can look for help on the Internet. In particular, look "
"through the <ulink url=\"https://basket-notepads.github.io\">old website</"
