"<quote>Tutorial: Basket: Capture your thoughts.</quote> Linux Format 120 "
"(Andy Channelle)"
msgstr ""
"<quote>Vadnica: Basket: Zajemite svoje misli.</quote> Linux Format 120 (Andy "
"Channelle)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
