"Basket</quote> Linux Magazine 54 (Stefanie Teufel)"
msgstr ""
"<quote>Virtualna košarica. Shranjevanje, razvrščanje in arhiviranje s KDE's "
"Basket</quote> Revija Linux 54 (Stefanie Teufel)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:56 index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "&basket; is mainly an all-purpose notes taker, but a particular one:"
msgstr "&basket; je večinoma večnamenski zapisovalnik, vendar še posebej:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using BasKet"
msgstr "Uporaba Basket-a"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Version Sync"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija različice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When enabled, Version Sync puts your baskets and notes under version "
"control. Currently this is an experimental feature and only very basic "
"functions are implemented, so it may require additional software and some "
"manual setup. These are some of the things that can be done using external "
"tools (but not Basket interface yet):"
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno, Version Sync postavi vaše košarice in opombe pod nadzor "
"različic. Trenutno je to poskusna funkcija in izvajajo se samo zelo osnovne "
"funkcije, zato bo morda zahtevala dodatno programsko opremo in nekaj ročnih "
"nastavitev. To je nekaj stvari, ki jih je mogoče narediti z zunanjimi orodji "
"(vendar še ne z vmesnikom Basket):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "check out old revisions and revert the changes"
msgstr "preverite stare revizije in razveljavite spremembe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "synchronize baskets on several computers (merge the changes)"
msgstr "sinhronizacija košaric na več računalnikih (spojitev sprememb)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "push baskets backup to remote repository"
msgstr "potisni varnostno kopijo košaric v oddaljeno skladišče"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enable it, select <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure BasKet Note Pads</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> → "
"<guibutton>Version Sync</guibutton> and <guibutton>Enable distributed "
"version control</guibutton>. It will initialize git repository in "
"<filename>~/.kde/share/apps/basket/baskets</filename>, upon which standard "
"git tools can be used."
msgstr ""
"Če ga želite omogočiti, izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj beležnice BasKet</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> → "
"<guibutton>Sinhronizacija različic</guibutton> in <guibutton>Omogoči "
"porazdeljeni nadzor različic</guibutton>. Inicializiral bo repozitorij git v "
"<filename>~/.kde/share/apps/basket/baskets</filename>, pri čemer je mogoče "
"uporabiti standardna orodja git."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clearing version history"
msgstr "Čiščenje zgodovine različic"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clearing the history can be useful in these cases:"
msgstr "Brisanje zgodovine je lahko koristno v teh primerih:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"you have locked a basket and want to remove any previous unencrypted "
"versions (which are still stored in the system)"
msgstr ""
"ste zaklenili košarico in želite odstraniti vse prejšnje nešifrirane "
"različice (ki so še vedno shranjene v sistemu)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"you want to free some disk space (can be topical if you insert a lot of "
"images or other files into Basket)"
msgstr ""
"želite sprostiti nekaj prostora na disku (lahko je aktualno, če v košarico "
"vstavljate veliko slik ali drugih datotek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that you will have to redo any manual setup you did on the git "
"repository."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da boste morali ponoviti vse ročne nastavitve, ki ste jih "
"izvedli v repozitoriju git."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "BasKet file structure"
msgstr "Struktura datoteke Basket"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "BasKet Archive file format"
msgstr "Format datoteke Basket Archive"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The BasKet file format (.baskets) is a structure which wraps a compressed "
"tar and a preview image. The latest archive format version is 0.6.1."
msgstr ""
"Datotečni format BasKet (.baskets) je struktura, ki ovije stisnjen tar in "
"sliko predogleda. Najnovejša različica zapisa arhiva je 0.6.1."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Structure"
msgstr "Struktura datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The archive file is divided into the structures: file header, preview image "
"header, a preview image (.png), archive header, and a gunzipped tar archive "
"(.tar.gz) containing a baskets file tree as illustrated in the following "
"sketch"
msgstr ""
"Arhivska datoteka je razdeljena na strukture: glava datoteke, glava slike za "
"predogled, slika za predogled (.png), glava arhiva in arhiviran arhiv tar (."
"tar.gz), ki vsebuje drevo datotek košaric, kot je prikazano na naslednji "
"skici"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive file header"
msgstr "Glava arhivske datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The file header is a short structure, consisting of lines of strings, the "
"file declarator, and the format version"
msgstr ""
"Glava datoteke je kratka struktura, sestavljena iz vrstic nizov, "
"deklaratorja datoteke in različice formata"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first 17 bytes contain the literal string <code>BasKetNP:archive</code> "
"followed by a new line feed symbol (0x0A) in ISO-8859-1 encoding."
msgstr ""
"Prvih 17 bajtov vsebuje dobesedni niz <code>BasKetNP:archive</code>, ki mu "
"sledi nov simbol za pomik vrstice (0x0A) v kodiranju ISO-8859-1."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The second string is a literal string <code>version:0.6.1</code> followed by "
"a line feed symbol (0x0A) in ISO-8859-1 encoding."
msgstr ""
"Drugi niz je dobesedni niz <code>version:0.6.1</code>, ki mu sledi simbol za "
"pomik vrstice (0x0A) v kodiranju ISO-8859-1."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126 index.docbook:134 index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "An example:"
msgstr "Primer:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<![CDATA[\n"
"BasKetNP:archive\n"
"version:0.6.1\n"
"                                                                        ]]>"
msgstr ""
"<![CDATA[\n"
"BasKetNP:archive\n"
"version:0.6.1\n"
"                                                                        ]]>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview image header"
msgstr "Predogled glave slike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Currently, the basket archive file contains a preview file which is derived "
"from the first basket's content."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno arhivska datoteka košarice vsebuje datoteko predogleda, ki izhaja "
"iz vsebine prve košarice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Directly following the file header, a literal string <code>preview*:&lt;"
"size&gt;</code> in ISO-8859-1 encoding, again followed by a line feed "
"symbol. The parameter <code>&lt;size&gt;</code> is a string of decimal "
"numbers. It declares the size in bytes of the preview image. <code>&lt;"
"size&gt;</code> is of type unsigned long."
msgstr ""
"Neposredno za glavo datoteke dobesedni niz <code>preview*:&lt;size&gt;</"
"code> v kodiranju ISO-8859-1, ki mu spet sledi simbol za pomik vrstice. "
"Parameter <code>&lt;size&gt;</code> je niz decimalnih števil. Deklarira "
"velikost predogledne slike v bajtih. <code>&lt;size&gt;</code> je vrste "
"unsigned long."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<![CDATA[\n"
"preview*:12000\n"
"                                                                        ]]>"
msgstr ""
"<![CDATA[\n"
"preview*:12000\n"
"                                                                        ]]>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview image file"
msgstr "Predogled slikovne datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The preview image is of type .png. Its size is specified by the preview "
"image header. The preview image file is inserted as file stream, and "
"directly follows the preview image header."
msgstr ""
"Slika za predogled je vrste .png. Njena velikost je določena z glavo "
"predogleda slike. Datoteka s sliko za predogled je vstavljena kot tok "
"datoteke in neposredno sledi glavi slike za predogled."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "BasKet content archive header"
msgstr "Glava arhiva vsebine Basket"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Just like for the preview image file, the content archive is preceded by a "
"string specifying its size. That string directly follows the file stream of "
"the archive."
msgstr ""
"Tako kot pri slikovni datoteki za predogled je pred arhivom vsebine niz, ki "
"določa njegovo velikost. Ta niz neposredno sledi datotečnemu toku arhiva."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"That string must be <code>archive*:&lt;size&gt;</code> followed by a line "
"feed symbol, in ISO-8869-1 encoding. The parameter <code>&lt;size&gt;</code> "
"is a unsigned long integer in string format."
msgstr ""
"Ta niz mora biti <code>archive*:&lt;size&gt;</code>, ki mu sledi simbol za "
"pomik vrstice, v kodiranju ISO-8869-1. Parameter <code>&lt;size&gt;</code> "
"je nepredznačeno dolgo celo število v obliki niza."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<![CDATA[\n"
"archive*:1245000\n"
"                                                                        ]]>"
msgstr ""
"<![CDATA[\n"
"archive*:1245000\n"
"                                                                        ]]>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "BasKet content archive"
msgstr "Arhiv vsebin Basket"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The content archive contains the BasKet file tree compressed in to a gzipped "
"tar archive (.tar.gz). Its size is specified by the content header."
msgstr ""
"Arhiv vsebine vsebuje datotečno drevo BasKet, stisnjeno v gzipiran arhiv tar "
"(.tar.gz). Njegova velikost je določena z glavo vsebine."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example byte stream"
msgstr "Primer toka bajtov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following table shows key parts of the basket archive file content. The "
"left column specifies the offset in the file stream. The center column gives "
"the byte stream at the current offset in hexadecimal format. The right "
"column shows printable characters within the file stream at the current "
"offset."
msgstr ""
"Naslednja tabela prikazuje ključne dele vsebine arhivske datoteke košarice. "
"Levi stolpec določa odmik v toku datoteke. Sredinski stolpec podaja tok "
"bajtov pri trenutnem odmiku v šestnajstiški obliki. Desni stolpec prikazuje "
"natisljive znake znotraj toka datoteke pri trenutnem odmiku."

